{"id":561231,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2017/06/【立此存照】孤独战士习近平/","date":"2017-06-14T06:16:15Z","modified":"2017-06-14T07:01:22Z","title":"【立此存照】“孤独战士”习近平","content":"<p>2017年6月8日，习近平与普京在哈萨克斯坦进行了会面。会议开始前，尴尬的一幕出现了：中方代表团因故全体迟到，导致一度只有习近平和随行的丁薛祥孤单地面对着包括普京在内的俄罗斯代表团。普京见习孤伶伶一人坐在对面（丁薛祥站在一边），笑着用俄语叫他“孤独战士”。</p>\n<p>俄罗斯官方媒体《今日俄罗斯》在 YouTube <a href=\"https://youtu.be/0nQKFTBmo5w\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">放出了</a>习近平独自一人尴尬面对俄国代表团的花絮。</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_561233\" style=\"width: 535px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/06/维尼1.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-561233\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/06/维尼1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"525\" height=\"295\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/06/维尼1.jpg 1707w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/06/维尼1-300x169.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/06/维尼1-768x431.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/06/维尼1-1024x575.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 525px) 100vw, 525px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080\">习近平独自一人入座；YouTube视频截图</span></p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_561234\" style=\"width: 535px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/06/维尼2.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-561234\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/06/维尼2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"525\" height=\"295\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/06/维尼2.jpg 1705w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/06/维尼2-300x169.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/06/维尼2-768x432.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/06/维尼2-1024x576.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 525px) 100vw, 525px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080\">普京笑得前俯后仰，习近平也只能陪笑；YouTube视频截图</span></p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_561235\" style=\"width: 535px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/06/维尼3-e1497418420439.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-561235\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/06/维尼3-e1497418420439.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"525\" height=\"294\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/06/维尼3-e1497418420439.jpg 1706w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/06/维尼3-e1497418420439-300x168.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/06/维尼3-e1497418420439-768x429.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/06/维尼3-e1497418420439-1024x573.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 525px) 100vw, 525px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080\">习近平尴尬地陪笑；YouTube视频截图</span></p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_561232\" style=\"width: 535px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/06/普京.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-561232\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/06/普京.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"525\" height=\"292\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/06/普京.jpg 1716w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/06/普京-300x167.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/06/普京-768x427.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/06/普京-1024x570.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 525px) 100vw, 525px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080\">面对“孤独战士”，普京笑成了一朵花；YouTube视频截图</span></p></div>\n<p>“孤独战士”相关新闻在中国大陆的社交网站上遭全面屏蔽，图片形式的微博也未被放过。以下为今天被删除的一则相关微博截图：</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_561249\" style=\"width: 460px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/06/download.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-561249\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/06/download.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"609\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/06/download.jpg 1204w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/06/download-222x300.jpg 222w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/06/download-768x1040.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/06/download-756x1024.jpg 756w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080\">被删微博截图</span></p></div>\n<p><strong>以下评论由数字时代编辑收集自新浪微博：</strong></p>\n<p>@九月九得酒：包包一定比较惊恐，以为发生政 变<img title=\"[哈哈]\" src=\"http://img.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/6a/laugh.gif\" alt=\"[哈哈]\" /></p>\n<p>@走X国师：背一篇书名就是了或者扛起桌子跑他个十里路<img title=\"[doge]\" src=\"http://img.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/b6/doge_org.gif\" alt=\"[doge]\" /></p>\n<p>@比较无聊的射手：这图片在微信群里已被屏蔽<img title=\"[二哈]\" src=\"http://img.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/74/moren_hashiqi_org.png\" alt=\"[二哈]\" /><img title=\"[并不简单]\" src=\"http://img.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/fc/moren_bbjdnew_org.png\" alt=\"[并不简单]\" /></p>\n<p>@i毛百万：视频里 老大只是含蓄（傻）和憨厚（笑）的含笑点头</p>\n<p>@灬少废话灬：突出领导，突出的过分了。</p>\n<p>@quchun：普京笑笑说：你是孤独的战士</p>\n<p>@WEI_Long_100：普京意有所指</p>\n<p>@卤肉饭再加个蛋：维尼熊大战俄国熊军团</p>\n<p>@乐园_乌贼：长者的俄语很熟练，连翻译都不用带。至于那个初中文化的那位嘛<img title=\"[并不简单]\" src=\"http://img.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/fc/moren_bbjdnew_org.png\" alt=\"[并不简单]\" /></p>\n<p>@石扉客2014:衔接出了问题</p>\n<p>@上党君：既然出现了外交漏洞，腹中有书怕个鸟儿，那就趁机和普京聊聊俄罗斯的文学名著，反正普京身边有翻译。</p>\n<p>@生拌牛肉沙拉：真·孤家寡人</p>\n<p>@肥仔梁曦掂过碌蔗:丢初中生的脸</p>\n<p>@行健小屋_3：让领导先走！</p>\n<p>积极努力自律：也许是真实写照吧</p>\n<p>@patiencepeace：这还得了，忠诚不绝对，绝对不忠诚啊。</p>\n<p><em><strong>附新华社对这次会面的报道：<a href=\"http://news.xinhuanet.com/world/2017-06/09/c_1121111904.htm\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">习近平会见俄罗斯总统普京</a></strong></em></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>那普京还在坏笑。</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_561242\" style=\"width: 460px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/06/0d4EWZ.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-561242\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/06/0d4EWZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"337\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/06/0d4EWZ.jpg 650w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/06/0d4EWZ-300x225.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080\">中方代表团抵达后的场面；网络图片</span></p></div>\n","author":980,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,19168,17016,27949],"tags":[25995,13222,14912,26242,14750]}